Introduction

Simon Dominic, previously known as Ssam D, K-OUTA & Simon D, is a South Korean rapper currently under Jay Park’s label, AOMG. He first appeared into the Korean hip-hop scene as K-OUTA, rapping underground in the early 2000’s, even being called the best rookie in the underground scene.
